
# 3) Optional: a tiny patch file (stubs only)

If you prefer a patch, save as `0001-hook-stubs.patch` and apply. Adjust the file path if your module lives elsewhere.

```diff
--- a/ProcessChatAI.module
+++ b/ProcessChatAI.module

@@
 class ProcessChatAI extends Process {
@@
+    /** Hook: mutate outbound request before sending to the model. */
+    public function ___beforeSend(array $request): array { return $request; }
+
+    /** Hook: inspect/mutate raw vendor response before normalization. */
+    public function ___afterSend(array $rawResponse): array { return $rawResponse; }
+
+    /** Hook: return optional HTML fragment for a contextual CTA (or null). */
+    public function ___composeCTA(array $ctx): ?string { return null; }
+
+    /** Hook: last-mile payload tweak before returning JSON to the widget. */
+    public function ___afterResponse(array $payload): array { return $payload; }
+
+    /** Helper hook: sites can override booking page detection. */
